Update on HIV-associated neurocognitive disorders. Curr Neurol Neurosci Rep
13, 387. 10.1007/s11910-013-0387-7</cite> [<a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/s11910-013-0387-7" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">DOI</a>] [<a href="/articles/PMC3784616/" class="usa-link">PMC free article</a>] [<a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23954972/" class="usa-link">PubMed</a>] [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=Curr%20Neurol%20Neurosci%20Rep&amp;title=Update%20on%20HIV-associated%20neurocognitive%20disorders&amp;author=T.%20B.%20Alfahad&amp;author=A.%20Nath&amp;volume=13&amp;publication_year=2013&amp;pages=387&amp;pmid=23954972&amp;doi=10.1007/s11910-013-0387-7&amp;" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Scholar</a>]</li>
